Previous editions referred to: Mitra_1866 (M), Fleet_1888 (F), Thaplyal_1985 (Th). Thaplyal seems to copy Fleet all or most of the time and will only be referred to if his reading differs from Fleet's. Mitra's readings will only be referred to if they are different from and not inferior to Fleet's.
