I don't have any decent image of this inscription when I'm doing the markup. Many things will need to be rechecked and supplied after getting BM photos and/or Fleet's rubbing. I'll use $ signs to show these.
--><!--
L1. $mangala symbol
--><lg n="1" met="śārdūlavikrīḍita">
