n="5"/>na mahā-ghoraḥ pratāpa-jvaraḥ||</l>
</lg>
<lg n="6" met="āryā">
<l n="ab">yasyātimānuṣaṁ karmma dr̥śyate vismayāj janaughena|</l>
<l n="cd">Adyāpi kośa-varddhana-taṭāt p<unclear>l</unclear>utaṁ pavana-jasyeva||</l><!--
